Once upon a time,there was a crocodile and a monkey.The monkey would take the mangoes for his friend crocodile.
The crocodile will then give the mangoes to her wife.The monkey and crocodile were very good friends.
The crocodile would give his wife most of it and will eat the remaining.
One day the crocodile's wife told him to take the monkey's heart so that she could eat it.
The crocodile  doesnt want to take the heart from the monkey, but his wife told him that she want the
monkey's heart for their aniversery so he had no choice.He went to search the monkey and eventually saw
him.He asked him for his heart but he said he left his heart aat home,then the crocodile went back home.